        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 2. Lithobius (Sinuispineus) sinuispineus sp. nov. (paratype female F, G; holotype H-L) F claw of female gonopod, ventral view G claw of female gonopod, dorsal view H posterior segments and gonopods in male, ventral view I posterior spurs of the femur of legs 15, dorsal view J posterior spurs of the femur of legs 15, ventral view K posterior spurs of the femur of legs 15, ventral view, showing minor teeth L tibia of legs 15 raised inward." , "Figure 1. Lithobius (Sinuispineus) sinuispineus sp. nov. (holotype A-D, paratype female E) A habitus, dorsal view B ocelli and Toemoesvary's organ (To), lateral view C cephalic plate, ventral view D forcipular coxosternite, ventral view E posterior segments and gonopods of female, ventral view." ;
